ales]] — as Litleo and its evolved form.\n* Litleo is the only Pokémon with a base stat total of 369.\n* The [[Litleonids|Litleonid meteor shower]] in [[Pokémon Omega Ruby and Alpha Sapphire]] is named after this Pokémon, a reference to the {{wp|Leonids|Leonid meteor shower}}.\n\n===Origin===\nLitleo is based on a lion cub.\n\n====Name origin====\nLitleo may be a combination of \'\'little\'\', \'\'lit\'\', and \'\'[[wiktionary:leo|leo]]\'\' (Latin for lion).\n\nShishiko is a combination of 獅子 \'\'shishi\'\' (lion) and 子 \'\'ko\'\' (child).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=fire|type2=normal\n|ja=シシコ \'\'Shishiko\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|獅子 \'\'shishi\'\'|lion}} and {{tt|子 \'\'ko\'\'|child}}\n|fr=Hélionceau|frmeaning=From \'\'{{wp|Helios}}\'\' and \'\'{{tt|lionceau|lion cub}}\'\'\n|es=Litleo|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Leufeo|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Leu|outdated term for lion}}\'\', \'\'{{tt|Feuer|fire}}\'\', and \'\'Leo\'\'\n|it=Litleo|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=레오꼬 \'\'Re\'okko\'\'|komeaning=From \'\'leo\'\' and {{tt|꼬마 \'\'kkoma\'\'|small child}}\n|zh_cmn=小獅獅 \'\'Xiǎoshīshī\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|小 \'\'xiǎo\'\'|little}} and {{tt|獅 \'\'shī\'\'|lion}}\n|zh_yue=小獅獅 \'\'Síusīsī\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=From {{tt|小 \'\'síu\'\'|little}} and {{tt|獅 \'\'sī\'\'|lion}}\n|hi=लिटलियो \'\'Litleo\'\'|himeaning=Transcription of English name\n|ru=Литлео \'\'Litleo\'\'|rumeaning=Transliteration English name\n}}\n{{-}}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Fire|type2=Normal}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Fire|prevnum=666|prev=Vivillon|nextnum=668|next=Pyroar}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Leufeo]]\n[[es:Litleo]]\n[[fr:Hélionceau]]\n[[it:Litleo]]\n[[ja:シシコ]]\n[[zh:小狮狮]]'}